main event: A UFO sighting was reported in Seattle, Washington on June 27, 1955.
interesting points: The sighting was ground-viewed and air-visual.
The object was observed for an unspecified length of time.
The object was reported to be flying parallel to the coast.
The original report was turned in to the USAF, but the source could not be contacted at the given address.
The case was deemed as having 'Insufficient Data for Evaluation' and was classified as 'Unknown'.
